<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include("./partials/head") %>
  <title>Support - Zipply</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/support.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("./partials/nav") %>

  <main class="support container">
    <div class="page-back-nav">
      <a href="/" class="page-back-link"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Back to Dashboard</a>
    </div>

    <section class="support__hero">
      <p class="support__eyebrow">SUPPORT</p>
      <h1 class="support__title">We're Here to Help</h1>
      <p class="support__subtitle">Find answers to common questions or get in touch with our team.</p>
      <p class="support__ist-clock" data-ist-clock>IST: --</p>
    </section>

    <section class="support__panel page-panel">
      <div class="support__content">
        <p class="support__intro"><strong>Need help with Zipply?</strong> Here are quick answers to the most common issues users face.</p>

        <h2>1. Shortened URL not working</h2>
        <p>Make sure the link is copied correctly. If the short link is expired or deleted, it will show a 404 page.</p>

        <h2>2. Clipboard button not working</h2>
        <p>Use a modern browser such as Chrome, Edge, Firefox, or Safari. Clipboard actions may fail in insecure contexts.</p>

        <h2>3. QR code still works after deletion</h2>
        <p>This is expected. QR codes encode the destination directly, so once generated they can still resolve even if records are deleted from dashboard history.</p>

        <h2>4. Analytics not showing</h2>
        <p>Check that you're signed in with the same account that created the link. Analytics are account-specific.</p>

        <h2>5. Payment failed</h2>
        <p>Verify your card or payment method details and try again. Payments are processed via Razorpay, and temporary gateway issues can also cause failures.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact Support</h2>
        <p>If your issue is still unresolved, contact us via:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:amanshow9800@gmail.com">amanshow9800@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aman-kumar-show-a5589b290" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/amanshow24" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p class="support__footer"><strong>Support hours:</strong> Responses are usually provided within 24 hours.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include("./partials/footer") %>
  <%- include("./partials/scripts") %>
</body>
</html>
